### Scripts for plotting estimates of diversity and divergence in 50 kb windows across the genome + tree weighting analysis



### Plotting tree weighting, Pi and Dxy

plotAngsdWindows_short_Pi_Dxy.R

requirements:
./data/output.weights.csv  		# results of tree weighting analysis
./data/formatBed_cumulated.tsv		# coordinates of windows for tree weighting analysis
./data/<ame1>_circos_tP.txt		# Pi for lineage
./data/<ame1.ame2>_circos_Dxy.txt	# Dxy for lineage



### Plotting tree weighting, Tajima's D and Fst	

plotAngsdWindows_short_Fst_Taj.R

requirements:
./data/output.weights.csv  		# results of tree weighting analysis
./data/formatBed_cumulated.tsv		# coordinates of windows for tree weighting analysis
./data/<ame1>_circos_Tajima.txt		# Tajima for lineage
./data/<ame1.ame2>_circos_FstW.txt	# Fst for lineage



